IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. HELLO-WORLD.
AUTHOR .HAWIN.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 N PIC 9(5).
01 REM PIC 9(2).
01 REV PIC 9(5) VALUE 0.
01 TEMP PIC 9(5).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
ACCEPT N.
MOVE N TO TEMP.
DISPLAY 'NUMBER: ' N
IF N>0
PERFORM UNTIL N=0
  COMPUTE REM = FUNCTION MOD(N 10)
  COMPUTE REV= (REV * 10) + REM
  COMPUTE N = N / 10
  
  END-PERFORM
END-IF
DISPLAY 'REVERSED: ' REV.

IF TEMP=REV
DISPLAY 'PALINDROME'
ELSE
DISPLAY 'NOT PALINDROME'
END-IF.
STOP RUN.
